
Building the samples for Android is a little more complicated at the moment. So execute the normal builde steps (waf configure, build) and then:

1. Do `cp build/debug/libbasicsample.so samples/android/libs/armeabi/`
2. Do `cd samples/android/`
3. Run `ANDROID_SDK_PATH/tools/android update project -p . -s --target android-17`
4. Run `ant debug`
5. Run `ANDROID_SDK_PATH/platform-tools/adb install bin/Gainput-simple-debug.apk`

Replace `ANDROID_NDK_PATH` and `ANDROID_SDK_PATH` with your local paths.

